If you have a problem using the skill, you can contact us by email :enquiries@frankolsenfurniture.co.uk. 

Download the Frank Olsen app from the Google Store or Apple store. Download the Alexa app and configure them. 

After connecting Alexa to your Frank Olsen products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Frank Olsen" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Frank Olsen account in our "Frank Olsen" app;
(3). You need to have some Frank Olsen devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Frank Olsen" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Frank Olsen Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Frank Olsen Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Frank Olsen Smart", and you'll be navigated to Frank Olsen login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

Then you can simply ask Alexa commanmds such as

"Alexa, set the light to blue" 
"Alexa, set the light to red" 
"Alexa, Turn on the light"
"Alexa, Turn off the light".

 Note: More functions can be controlled through the app.
